  "leve": {
    "name": "Don't Bore Me, Ore Me",
    "description": "Because my brother and I forge a wide variety of weapons, we often find ourselves low on materials. And so we turn to the Pelupelu and their merchants, who love to talk us into some deal or another. If I have to hear one more smooth sales pitch, I may be tempted to use my hammer for ill. For the sake of peace in Tuliyollal's markets, might I ask for a delivery of ingots? Crafted quietly, if you please!",
